rce/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999859012985124, \"rank\": 1.0357636689699346e-05, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"43.44 seconds\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 249, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"his own lifetime\", \"from\": 291, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"43.40 seconds\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It meant another agonising second place on the world stage for Hudson-Smith, who missed gold by just 0.09 seconds at the World Athletics Championships 12 months ago.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 497, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 453, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999992037374, \"rank\": 7.30901904869674e-10, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another agonising second place\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 371}, {\"ngram\": \"the world stage\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 390}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 407}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"just 0.09 seconds\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he also failed to match his former housemate Lyles,after the American landed 100m gold on Sunday.\", \"from\": 499, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9999320827482758, \"rank\": 5.431243330476316e-05, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"100m gold\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking toEurosporton Thursday morning, Hudson-Smith was asked if he had received any messages from Lyles, who is still aiming for a sprint double having reached the 200m final.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9999320827482758, \"rank\": 5.431243330476316e-05, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toEurosporton\", \"from\": 611, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"any messages\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 697}, {\"ngram\": \"sprint\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He messaged me beforehand and it was, well, I did not read it because I was just so focussed on like the task at hand,\\\" he admitted.\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the task\", \"from\": 883, \"to\": 891}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 899}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pressed on whether he'd since read the message and replied, Hudson-Smith claimed: \\\"I still have not had the chance to read it.\\\"\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 962}, {\"ngram\": \"Hudson-Smith\", \"from\": 976, \"to\": 988}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1020, \"to\": 1030}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One presenter then joked: \\\"You ghosted Noah Lyles?\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1083, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", 